OL,5, Sir Ian McKellen is to appear in a new 
OL,6, play which blends parts one and two of 
OL,7, Shakespeare's Henry IV.                
OL,9,FThe actor will play John Falstaff, a   
OL,10,Fcharacter he has never portrayed       
OL,11,Fdespite appearing in a huge number of  
OL,12,FShakespeare plays throughout his life. 
OL,14,FDirector Robert Icke's production of   
OL,15,FPlayer Kings will play in Manchester   
OL,16,Fand London next year.                  
OL,18,FSir Ian told BBC News the offer to     
OL,19,Fappear in the "ingenious adaptation"   
OL,20,Fwas "irresistible".                    
